text: "Holy Grail" is a 1993 song by Australian rock band Hunters & Collectors and is the fifth single from their seventh studio album Cut. It went to number 20 in Australia and number 25 in New Zealand and was released in the United Kingdom in 1994. It has become a very popular sports anthem since its release and is the theme song to the Queensland cricket team in the Sheffield Shield. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1993 songs Category:Rock songs Category:Pub rock songs Category:Hunters & Collectors songs
